{"tid":681621,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"(WTS)搞左四年既員工折扣互相分享群","createTime":"2018-05-28T07:51:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-07T07:05:32.000Z","uid":75218,"like":6,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":64,"replies":[{"pid":"e18d285c51da64fc4a5fb7674a8ca328336e65b0","tid":681621,"uid":75218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T07:51:51.000Z","msg":"為左繼續擴大我地群組擁有既折扣,依家又黎第N次招攬新人加入啦 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBackground:<br />\n<br />\n1.依家大概有650人,分開左3個wts群<br />\n2. 建立左 4 年<br />\n3. 只要係group入面打自己想要既折扣, admin / 其他會員就會協助你<br />\n4. 咁多人都仲要加係因為不斷會有 pt唔做, 同埋唔夠多名牌折扣 <br />\n<br />\n我地需要既人<br />\n<br />\n1. 有員工既優惠提供, 並且樂意幫番人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2. 暫時不接受 保險,地產經紀<br />\n3. 會多d上水 就最好<br />\n4. 唔接受VIP discount ,生日優惠<br />\n5. 先小人後君子, 如發現 抽水/蓄意唔幫人/根本無呢個折扣 即踢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有興趣既朋友係度入番d資料, 應承大家14日內加一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScFmIMGvh3DsoEvnyM2kQ5EccV7LE3JvQrYoMpTJLGsBKNx5w/viewform?c=0&amp;w=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLScFmIMGvh3DsoEvnyM2kQ5EccV7LE3JvQrYoMpTJLGsBKNx5w%2Fviewform%3Fc%3D0%26w%3D1&d=bFYDW4yt9lkxTqnDWxBjIsPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=2bfa9fd4\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScFmIMGvh3DsoEvnyM2kQ5EccV7LE3JvQrYoMpTJLGsBKNx5w/viewform?c=0&amp;w=1</a>"},{"pid":"9a1128294e4d62546995844e7139778e0dfdff48","tid":681621,"uid":75218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T11:11:37.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"178ed577be5e33d6fbe46cfe02ecf3e30bc83235","tid":681621,"uid":75218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-28T17:54:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0f832cfa83b3c78ce76ac688bb46266cbb449b9c","tid":681621,"uid":13446,"like":0,